verbose_text: According to the lncRNA-miRNA-mRNA sub network, we speculated that these 4 lncRNAs might have a decisive role in altering the expression of the downstream KIRC related disease mRNAs through competitive interactions with miRNAs (miR-21, miR-155, miR-221, and miR-223).
